<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>MommyGlow • Pregnancy Care</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Dancing+Script:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.6.0/css/all.min.css" />

  <style>
    :root {
      --pink: #e91e63;
      --pink-dark: #c2185b;
      --pink-light: #fce4ec;
      --text: #444;
      --bg: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff5f8 0%, #fce4ec 50%, #f8bbd0 100%);
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.7;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* Clean Header - Fixed & Glassy */
    header {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.1);
      padding: 18px 50px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      z-index: 1000;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.12);
    }
    .logo {
      font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
      font-size: 40px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--pink);
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    /* Dark & Premium Buttons */
    .nav-btn {
      padding: 12px 28px;
      margin-left: 12px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15px;
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }
    .login {
      background: #333;
      color: white;
    }
    .signup {
      background: var(--pink);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.4);
    }
    .nav-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    .signup:hover {
      background: var(--pink-dark);
    }

    /* Main Content */
    main {
      padding: 140px 20px 100px;
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 4.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--pink-dark);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      animation: softGlow 4s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }
    @keyframes softGlow {
      from { text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(233,30,99,0.3); }
      to { text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(233,30,99,0.5); }
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: #666;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto 70px;
    }

    /* Hero Image */
    .hero-img {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto 90px;
      border-radius: 34px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 25px 70px rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.25);
    }
    .hero-img img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
      transition: transform 0.8s ease;
    }
    .hero-img:hover img { transform: scale(1.08); }

    /* Section Titles */
    h2 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: var(--pink-dark);
      margin: 90px 0 60px;
      position: relative;
    }
    h2::after {
      content: '';
      width: 120px;
      height: 5px;
      background: var(--pink);
      display: block;
      margin: 20px auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    /* Clean Cards */
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: 35px;
      margin-bottom: 100px;
    }
    .card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 40px 25px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.15);
      transition: all 0.5s ease;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-15px);
      box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.25);
    }
    .card i {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      color: var(--pink);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .card h3 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      color: var(--pink-dark);
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    /* Month Cards */
    .months {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(340px, 1fr));
      gap: 40px;
      padding: 0 20px 120px;
    }
    .month-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 32px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.2);
      transition: all 0.6s ease;
    }
    .month-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-20px);
      box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.3);
    }
    .month-card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 240px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }
    .month-info {
      padding: 28px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .month h3 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: var(--pink-dark);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      h1 { font-size: 3.2rem; }
      h2 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
      header { padding: 15px 20px; }
      .nav-btn { padding: 10px 20px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="logo">MommyGlow</div>
    <div>
      <a href="/login" class="nav-btn login">Login</a>
      <a href="/signup" class="nav-btn signup">Join Free</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <h1>Your Beautiful Journey Begins</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Expert guidance, month-by-month baby growth tracker, and loving care tips for you and your little one.</p>

    <div class="hero-img">
      <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/4422629/pexels-photo-4422629.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1" alt="Pregnant Mom">
    </div>

    <h2>Essential Pregnancy Care</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i><h3>Healthy Diet</h3><p>Rich in folic acid, iron & protein</p></div>
      <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-tint"></i><h3>Stay Hydrated</h3><p>3–4 liters water daily</p></div>
      <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-walking"></i><h3>Light Exercise</h3><p>Walk & prenatal yoga</p></div>
      <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-stethoscope"></i><h3>Regular Checkups</h3><p>Never miss doctor visits</p></div>
      <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-ban"></i><h3>Avoid Harmful</h3><p>No alcohol, smoking, stress</p></div>
      <div class="card"><i class="fas fa-heart"></i><h3>Rest & Love</h3><p>Sleep well, stay happy</p></div>
    </div>

    <h2>Baby's Growth Month by Month</h2>
    <div class="months">
      <div class="month-card"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/2908177/pexels-photo-2908177.jpeg" alt="Month 1"><div class="month"><h3>Month 1</h3><p>Heartbeat begins</p></div></div>
      <div class="month-card"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/4057644/pexels-photo-4057644.jpeg" alt="Month 2"><div class="month"><h3>Month 2</h3><p>Organs form</p></div></div>
      <div class="month-card"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3770589/pexels-photo-3770589.jpeg" alt="Month 3"><div class="month"><h3>Month 3</h3><p>Arms & legs move</p></div></div>
      <div class="month-card"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3905255/pexels-photo-3905255.jpeg" alt="Month 4"><div class="month"><h3>Month 4</h3><p>First kicks!</p></div></div>
      <div class="month-card"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/4057650/pexels-photo-4057650.jpeg" alt="Month 5"><div class="month"><h3>Month 5</h3><p>Hears your voice</p></div></div>
      <div class="month-card"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/4439421/pexels-photo-4439421.jpeg" alt="Month 6"><div class="month"><h3>Month 6</h3><p>Eyes open</p></div></div>
      <div class="month-card"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/4449682/pexels-photo-4449682.jpeg" alt="Month 7"><div class="month"><h3>Month 7</h3><p>Lungs develop</p></div></div>
      <div class="month-card"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/4057663/pexels-photo-4057663.jpeg" alt="Month 8"><div class="month"><h3>Month 8</h3><p>Gaining weight</p></div></div>
      <div class="month-card"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/4057670/pexels-photo-4057670.jpeg" alt="Month 9"><div class="month"><h3>Month 9</h3><p>Ready to meet you!</p></div></div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>